"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(Laboratory.ID)\nFROM Patient\nJOIN Laboratory ON Patient.ID = Laboratory.ID\nWHERE Patient.First_Date = '1991-06-13'\n  AND Patient.Diagnosis = 'SJS'\n  AND Laboratory.Date BETWEEN '1995-01-01' AND '1995-12-31';\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the total number of laboratory tests for a patient who first came to the hospital on June 13, 1991, and was diagnosed with SJS, specifically for tests conducted in the year 1995."